      <p>
          Non blandit massa enim nec dui nunc mattis enim ut. Ante metus dictum at tempor commodo ullamcorper. Mattis pellentesque id nibh tortor. Mauris commodo quis imperdiet massa tincidunt nunc pulvinar sapien. Sit amet aliquam id diam maecenas ultricies. Fringilla urna porttitor rhoncus dolor purus non enim. Malesuada fames ac turpis egestas integer eget aliquet nibh. Faucibus a pellentesque sit amet porttitor eget dolor morbi. Ut pharetra sit amet aliquam. Et sollicitudin ac orci phasellus egestas tellus rutrum tellus. Et malesuada fames ac turpis egestas sed tempus urna. Consequat interdum varius sit amet mattis.
      </p>
      <p class="pricing-title mt-5 mb-4">{{ 'home.price.title'|trans|raw }}</p>
      <div class="row">
          <div class="col-md-4 col-lg-4">
              <div class="card mb-3">
                  <div class="card-header">
                      {{ 'subscription.type_free'|trans|raw }}
                  </div>
                  <div class="card-body">
                      <span class="card-title">Discover the website</span>
                      <hr>
                      <h6 class="card-text">Features limited</h6>
                  </div>
              </div>
          </div>
          <div class="col-md-4 col-lg-4">
              <div class="card mb-3">
                  <div class="card-header">
                      {{ 'subscription.type_occasional'|trans|raw }}
                  </div>
                  <div class="card-body">
                      <span class="card-title">8,99 &euro;</span>
                      <span class="frequency"> / semaine</span>
                      <hr>
                      <h6 class="card-text">Engagement minimum de 1 semaine</h6>
                  </div>
              </div>
          </div>
          <div class="col-md-4 col-lg-4">
              <div class="card mb-3">
                  <div class="card-header">
                      {{ 'subscription.type_punctual'|trans|raw }}
                  </div>
                  <div class="card-body">
                      <span class="card-title">28,99 &euro;</span>
                      <span class="frequency"> / mois</span>
                      <hr>
